{
  "name": "Research Proposal Template",
  "description": "Research proposal template for grant applications or thesis proposals",
  "category": "research",
  "discipline": "general",
  "content": {
    "title": "Research Proposal: [Your Project Title]",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "Executive Summary"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Brief overview of your proposed research (1-2 paragraphs). Include the research problem, objectives, methodology, and expected outcomes."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "1. Introduction"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "content": "1.1 Background and Context"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Provide background information on the research area. Explain why this research is important now."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "content": "1.2 Problem Statement"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Clearly define the problem or gap in knowledge that your research will address."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "2. Research Questions and Objectives"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "content": "2.1 Primary Research Question"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "State your main research question."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "content": "2.2 Specific Objectives"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "List 3-5 specific, measurable objectives that your research will accomplish."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "3. Literature Review"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Review key existing research related to your topic. Demonstrate your understanding of the field and identify the gap your research will fill."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "4. Theoretical Framework"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Describe the theoretical foundation for your research. What theories or models will guide your work?"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "5. Methodology"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "content": "5.1 Research Design"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Outline your research approach and design."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "content": "5.2 Participants/Sample"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Describe your target population and sampling strategy."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "content": "5.3 Data Collection Methods"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Explain how you will collect data (instruments, procedures, timeline)."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "content": "5.4 Data Analysis"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Describe how you will analyze the data."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "6. Expected Outcomes and Significance"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "What do you expect to find? How will your research contribute to the field?"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "7. Timeline"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Provide a realistic timeline for completing each phase of your research."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "8. Budget (if applicable)"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Itemized budget showing how funds will be used."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "9. Ethical Considerations"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Discuss any ethical issues and how you will address them. Include IRB/ethics approval plans."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 1,
        "content": "References"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "[Your references will be automatically formatted here]"
      }
    ]
  }
}
